document.title: Welcome to Our Blog
document.author: John Doe
document.description: Welcome to our blog where we share insights about technology and development.

body.raw:
# Welcome to Our Blog

This is our first blog post using markdown. Here's what you can do with markdown:

## Features

- Write content in a simple, readable format
- Use **bold** and _italic_ text
- Create lists and code blocks
- Add links and images

## Code Example

```typescript
function greet(name: string) {
  return `Hello, ${name}!`;
}
```

## What's Next?

Stay tuned for more posts about:

- Web Development
- Best Practices
- Tips and Tricks
